</p>
</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA12d015n1-ptr" id="PJA12d015n1">1</a>
<p><abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> is responding to James Lovells letter of <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-11-02-0282" class="document">21 June</a> (vol. 11:381383).</p>
</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA12d015n2-ptr" id="PJA12d015n2">2</a>
<p>For the plight of Samuel Curson and Isaac Gouverneur Jr. and an account of the letters entrusted to them, see vol. <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-11-02-0327" class="document">11:440442</a>.</p>
